The word "Data" must be removed from the course title.There is zero mentions of any form of data in the entirity of the course.  There is a peer graded assignment in the end that definitely is a mere placeholder, and it is not even mandatory. 
What a waste of time.

The caculus part is mediocre as well.
Excellent teacher and materials. All the exercises are useful for my Calculus class in university!
amazing course with tons of concrete examples, great lecturer, very clear teaching, would highly recommend to anyone who want to learn calculus
This is a great course. Instructor is amazing and goes through a large number of examples.
